OL,3,CFamily's 'nightmare' after man drowns
OL,4,Cin freak paddling pool accident
OL,6,FThe family of a man who drowned after
OL,7,Ffalling into a paddling pool in a
OL,8,Ffreak accident are warning people not
OL,9,Fto take the dangers of water for
OL,10,Fgranted.
OL,12,FRoan Bloore, 24, is thought to have
OL,13,Feither passed out or lost his footing
OL,14,Fand fell face down into just nine
OL,15,Finches of water at his home in
OL,16,FDoncaster when emptying the pool last
OL,17,Fmonth.
