OL,3,CFamily's 'nightmare' after man drowns
OL,4,Cin freak paddling pool accident
OL,6,FHe was in the water for around ten
OL,7,Fminutes before he was found by a
OL,8,Ffamily friend who was in the house at
OL,9,Fthe time.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called and,
OL,12,Fafter an hour of CPR, paramedics
OL,13,Fmanaged to restart his heart but he
OL,14,Fdied later in hospital.
OL,16,FHis father Michael Bloore said: "It's
OL,17,Fa nightmare that you just can't wake
OL,18,Fup from. Twenty-four years - it's not
OL,19,Feven a quarter of a century.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
