OL,3,CFamily's 'nightmare' after man drowns
OL,4,Cin freak paddling pool accident
OL,6,F"It's as soon as I wake up, the tears
OL,7,Fstart. Then I try and focus on things
OL,8,Fthat need to keep the house running,
OL,9,Ftidying up mostly. I can't do a lot of
OL,10,Fit because it hurts.
OL,12,F"I'm disabled and I like to go
OL,13,Feverywhere with somebody else in case
OL,14,FI have a problem. So he used to act as
OL,15,Fmy carer, he used to go to the shop
OL,16,Fwith me, help me carry stuff. He was
OL,17,Fso caring."
