OL,3,CFamily's 'nightmare' after man drowns
OL,4,Cin freak paddling pool accident
OL,6,FRoan's family were on holiday in Devon
OL,7,Fwhen the accident happened and raced
OL,8,Fback to Doncaster after hearing what
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FBut they were too late to say their
OL,12,Ffinal goodbyes.
OL,14,FMichael said: "It's horrible. It's
OL,15,Fjust not something you'd ever think
OL,16,Fwould happen to you."
OL,18,F"Unfortunately we were about 10
OL,19,Fminutes late, before his heart
OL,20,Fstopped. So we just missed it. He'd
OL,21,Falready gone by the time we got back."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
