OL,3,CFamily's 'nightmare' after man drowns
OL,4,Cin freak paddling pool accident
OL,6,FRoan's family are now warning others
OL,7,Fabout the dangers of paddling pools
OL,8,Fand think if someone had been with him
OL,9,Fat the time he would still be alive
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FMichael said: "I"m just so gutted that
OL,13,Fhe decided to empty the pool on his
OL,14,Fown. If he'd said to my friend, 'here
OL,15,Fhelp me with this'. It might not have
OL,16,Fhappened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
