OL,3,CFamily's 'nightmare' after man drowns
OL,4,Cin freak paddling pool accident
OL,6,F"No matter how deep water is, it can
OL,7,Fbe dangerous. So my advice is always
OL,8,Fwork in pairs at least. We just don't
OL,9,Fwant to see anybody else get hurt from
OL,10,Fa paddling pool at any age."
OL,12,FRoan's older brother Deklan, who is a
OL,13,Ffully qualified lifeguard, said: "It
OL,14,Ftakes 30 seconds for somebody to
OL,15,Fdrown, that's with them already face
OL,16,Fdown in the water. All it takes is a
OL,17,Fteaspoon of water to enter somebody's
OL,18,Flungs and that could kill them."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
